<!--<h4>First piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī jayābhyudaya śakavaruṣaṁbulu 12<unclear>9</unclear>2 Agunēṁṭi sādhāraṇa saṁvatsara puśya śu 5 lu yarabhairajiyyala koḍuku pappajiyyalu cētanu <unclear>dēvikāmana</unclear> Ā pappajiyyalakuṁ jellē bhairava dēvara vritti pālu <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> pappajiyyalaku Aidu Ā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="2"/>kāmana peṭina varahāni kaṁparāju Õ650 Akṣarālānu Ivē Āṟunūṭa yēbayi[Ī] śāsanānaku sākṣulu pallaka bhairajiyyala koḍuku bōlajiyyalānu pāpajiyyalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kāṭajiyya<unclear>la</unclear> mallijiyyalānu ceṁnnaka malli jiyyalānu Anaṁta
</p>

<!--<h4>Third piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="3"/>ṁ kōmanaku mūḍa cālluṁ Ā mūṁḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> gā goni <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>raṁ vriti malliseṭṭi taṁmuḍu kayyavāgi seṭṭiṁni vaṭnūri mūla<unclear>stānaṁ vārunu</unclear>
</p>

